 party in Ondo state should be guided accordingly,” the statement further added. Vanguard Nigeria News The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has extended the deadline for the sale and collection of Presidential, Governorship and National Assembly nomination forms from the earlier announced date of Thursday, September 6, 2018 to Monday, September 10, 2018. September 5, 2018 In "News" By Omeiza Ajayi The ruling All Progressives Congress, APC, has announced Monday, June 22 and Monday, July 20 for its governorship primary elections in Edo and Ondo states. This came as the Independent National Electoral Commission, INEC, said it would stick to its timetable and schedule of activities regarding the elections… May 19, 2020 In "Politics" By Omeiza Ajayi ABUJA - The ruling All Progressives Congress APC has announced Monday, June 22 and Monday, July 20 for its governorship primary elections in Edo and Ondo states. This came as the Independent National Electoral Commission INEC said it would stick to its timetable and schedule of activities… May 20, 2020 In "Politics"